<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 21:14:21 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>墨西哥下议院批准针对应用程序工人的劳动改革</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/mexicos-lower-house-approves-labor-reform-app-workers-2024-12-10/</link><description>墨西哥下议院周二批准了一项改革，旨在通过确保获得社会保障和圣诞奖金等福利来规范滴滴、Rappi 和 Uber 等应用程序的送货员和司机的劳动条件。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 21:04:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/mexicos-lower-house-approves-labor-reform-app-workers-2024-12-10/</guid></item><item><title>瑞穗董事小林表示企业不应对特朗普的关税威胁反应过度</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/mizuho-director-kobayashi-says-companies-should-not-overreact-trumps-tariff-2024-12-10/</link><description>日本瑞穗金融、欧姆龙和全日空的董事小林泉周二表示，企业不应对当选总统唐纳德·特朗普对中国商品征收关税的威胁反应过度。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 19:10:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/mizuho-director-kobayashi-says-companies-should-not-overreact-trumps-tariff-2024-12-10/</guid></item><item><title>美国因可能致命的勒索软件攻击而制裁中国公司</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/us-sanctions-chinese-firm-over-potentially-deadly-ransomware-attack-2024-12-10/</link><description>美国因一家中国网络安全公司实施了一次雄心勃勃的网络攻击而对其实施制裁，美国财政部官员称该攻击可能导致人员死亡。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 16:43:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/us-sanctions-chinese-firm-over-potentially-deadly-ransomware-attack-2024-12-10/</guid></item><item><title>美国因人权问题对两家中国企业实施贸易限制</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-imposes-trade-restrictions-two-chinese-firms-over-human-rights-2024-12-10/</link><description>周二，美国将两家中国公司列入贸易限制名单，理由是它们涉嫌助长侵犯人权行为，而总统乔·拜登在其执政的最后几天继续向北京施压。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 15:04:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-imposes-trade-restrictions-two-chinese-firms-over-human-rights-2024-12-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国复星旅文将通过回购股份实现私有化</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-fosun-take-tourism-unit-private-125-bln-deal-2024-12-10/</link><description>中国复星旅文拟回购非控股股东持有的股份，以实现私有化并解决对其股票流动性有限的担忧。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 10:58:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-fosun-take-tourism-unit-private-125-bln-deal-2024-12-10/</guid></item><item><title>光大集团原董事长因贪污受贿被判有期徒刑12年</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-everbright-group-former-chairman-jailed-12-years-corruption-bribery-2024-12-10/</link><description>据中央电视台周二报道，中国光大集团原董事长唐双宁因贪污、受贿、滥用职权罪被判处有期徒刑12年。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 09:15:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-everbright-group-former-chairman-jailed-12-years-corruption-bribery-2024-12-10/</guid></item><item><title>STOXX 600 结束八连胜；欧洲央行决策成为焦点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/european-shares-slip-after-china-stimulus-excitement-wanes-focus-us-cpi-2024-12-10/</link><description>斯托克 600 指数周二收低，结束了连续八个交易日的上涨势头，中国贸易数据疲弱后，奢侈品股领跌，而投资者则等待欧洲央行本周晚些时候的政策决定。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 08:29:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/european-shares-slip-after-china-stimulus-excitement-wanes-focus-us-cpi-2024-12-10/</guid></item><item><title>Stellantis与中国宁德时代将投资43.3亿美元在西班牙建设电动汽车电池工厂</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/stellantis-chinas-catl-invest-433-bln-ev-battery-factory-spain-2024-12-10/</link><description>受较低成本和政府资助的鼓励，Stellantis 和中国电池制造商 CATL 将投资 41 亿欧元（43.3 亿美元）在西班牙建设欧洲最大的电动汽车电池工厂之一。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 08:25:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/stellantis-chinas-catl-invest-433-bln-ev-battery-factory-spain-2024-12-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国对俄罗斯出口四个月来首次下降</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/chinas-exports-russia-drop-first-time-four-months-2024-12-10/</link><description>中国海关周二公布的数据显示，11 月份中国对俄罗斯的人民币计价出口出现两位数下降，较 10 月份 24% 的增长大幅恶化，并且是四个月来首次下降。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 08:10:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/chinas-exports-russia-drop-first-time-four-months-2024-12-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国宁德时代拟与Stellantis在西班牙成立价值40亿美元的电池合资公司</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-catl-plans-set-up-4-bln-battery-jv-spain-with-stellantis-2024-12-10/</link><description>根据宁德时代周二提交的股票文件，中国电动汽车巨头宁德时代计划与西班牙 Stellantis 成立一家电池合资企业。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 08:06:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-catl-plans-set-up-4-bln-battery-jv-spain-with-stellantis-2024-12-10/</guid></item><item><title>太平洋岛国等待特朗普，对气候和中国立场保持警惕</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/pacific-islands-wait-trump-wary-climate-china-stance-2024-12-10/</link><description>外交官表示，太平洋岛国是美国和中国之间战略竞争的中心，这些国家带来了基础设施和资金，希望当选总统唐纳德·特朗普继续参与该地区事务，但担心竞争演变成对抗。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 08:02:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/pacific-islands-wait-trump-wary-climate-china-stance-2024-12-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国因“干涉”香港事务而宣布对美国人员实施签证限制</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-announces-visa-restrictions-us-personnel-over-hong-kong-interference-2024-12-10/</link><description>中国外交部周二在新闻发布会上表示，中国决定对一些在涉港问题上“表现恶劣”、“干涉”香港事务的美国人员实施签证限制。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 07:48:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-announces-visa-restrictions-us-personnel-over-hong-kong-interference-2024-12-10/</guid></item><item><title>中国准备进一步举债以对抗特朗普的关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-ready-go-deeper-into-debt-counter-trumps-tariffs-2024-12-10/</link><description>中国领导人在十多年来最温和的声明之一中表示，他们准备采取一切必要的刺激措施，以应对美国预期的贸易关税对明年经济增长的影响。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 07:43:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-ready-go-deeper-into-debt-counter-trumps-tariffs-2024-12-10/</guid></item><item><title>星巴克任命首位中国首席增长官 - 媒体</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/starbucks-appoints-first-china-chief-growth-officer-media-2024-12-10/</link><description>据中国媒体《晚报》周二报道，星巴克中国任命了首位首席增长官（CGO）。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 07:40:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/starbucks-appoints-first-china-chief-growth-officer-media-2024-12-10/</guid></item><item><title>贸易商称，中国恒力利用额外进口配额从道达尔购买中东石油</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chinas-hengli-uses-extra-import-quota-buy-mideast-oil-total-traders-say-2024-12-10/</link><description>六名知情交易员表示，中国私营炼油商恒力石化已抢购中东原油，其中大部分来自法国石油巨头TotalEnergies，此前这家法国巨头囤积了大量石油，且伊朗对中国的供应收紧。</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 06:11:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/chinas-hengli-uses-extra-import-quota-buy-mideast-oil-total-traders-say-2024-12-10/</guid></item></channel></rss>